00:09:13.511 --> 00:09:14.387
then you know it's a thing.

00:09:14.387 --> 00:09:15.846
So it's it's

00:09:15.846 --> 00:09:17.473
and that's what happened to me time

00:09:17.473 --> 00:09:19.100
after time over a couple of years.

00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:20.184
So like,

00:09:20.184 --> 00:09:21.978
there wasn't a singular moment

00:09:21.978 --> 00:09:23.020
where you're like,

00:09:23.020 --> 00:09:25.147
just open the folder and you go,

00:09:25.147 --> 00:09:26.399
What the fuck is that?

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:27.817
It was kind of like

00:09:27.817 --> 00:09:30.069
a slow burn culmination

00:09:30.069 --> 00:09:32.071
as I was processing it,

00:09:32.071 --> 00:09:32.905
you know,

00:09:32.905 --> 00:09:33.739
allowing my world

00:09:33.739 --> 00:09:36.075
view to open and yeah,

00:09:36.075 --> 00:09:37.702
I don't know
if there was a singular moment.

00:09:37.702 --> 00:09:38.828
I think it was, you know,

00:09:38.828 --> 00:09:39.495
some of the really,

00:09:39.495 --> 00:09:41.122
really trusted

00:09:41.122 --> 00:09:42.999
high level people we talked to

00:09:42.999 --> 00:09:43.958
when they, you know,

00:09:43.958 --> 00:09:45.376
stared us straight in the face

00:09:45.376 --> 00:09:47.253
very seriously.

00:09:47.253 --> 00:09:48.296
And, you know,

00:09:48.296 --> 00:09:49.755
confirmed a lot of this information

00:09:49.755 --> 00:09:51.966
and the quality of people we talked to,

00:09:51.966 --> 00:09:54.302
if they ever go public,

00:09:54.385 --> 00:09:56.846
it'll blow your mind who we talked to.

00:09:56.846 --> 00:09:57.388
I was like, wow,

00:09:57.388 --> 00:09:59.307
I can't believe I'm talking to X,

00:09:59.307 --> 00:10:01.225
who's a really important person.

00:10:01.225 --> 00:10:02.101
And they're confirming

00:10:02.101 --> 00:10:03.436
these certain details

00:10:03.436 --> 00:10:04.937
and they're saying like, you know,

00:10:04.937 --> 00:10:06.355
we need to protect us at all costs.

00:10:06.355 --> 00:10:06.897
They're giving me kind

00:10:06.897 --> 00:10:08.899
of the whole speech about it.

00:10:08.899 --> 00:10:10.026
And I'm sitting there, it's

00:10:10.026 --> 00:10:11.319
like an out of body experience.

00:10:11.319 --> 00:10:13.863
I'm like, okay, well, this is a thing.

00:10:17.325 --> 00:10:18.909
I don't report to anybody

00:10:18.909 --> 00:10:21.078
and there is no plan.

00:10:21.078 --> 00:10:21.871
I'm not a part of some

00:10:21.871 --> 00:10:24.165
like slow drip disclosure or anything.

00:10:24.165 --> 00:10:25.541
If there is a plan, I'm

00:10:25.541 --> 00:10:27.460
totally unwitting and holy shit,

00:10:27.460 --> 00:10:28.210
they've like,

00:10:28.210 --> 00:10:30.421
controlled me in a very passive manner

00:10:30.421 --> 00:10:31.756
that is like masterclass,

00:10:31.756 --> 00:10:33.883
but yeah, I'm

00:10:33.883 --> 00:10:35.551
not a part of some weird shit,

00:10:35.551 --> 00:10:36.510
you know that.

00:10:36.510 --> 00:10:38.304
Did you ever, at any point

00:10:38.304 --> 00:10:39.513
try to suss out

00:10:39.513 --> 00:10:41.015
whether you were being lied to?

00:10:41.015 --> 00:10:42.266
Because all of these people

00:10:42.266 --> 00:10:44.435
are coming from the same programs

00:10:44.435 --> 00:10:45.394
and so presumably

00:10:45.394 --> 00:10:46.687
there's some level of coordination

00:10:46.687 --> 00:10:47.313
between them.

00:10:47.313 --> 00:10:48.230
So how do you kind of

00:10:48.230 --> 00:10:49.273
get through - Yeah.

00:10:49.273 --> 00:10:51.734
And just make sure that they're not

00:10:51.734 --> 00:10:53.110
meeting in some back room saying,

00:10:53.110 --> 00:10:54.028
you say this to Dave,

00:10:54.028 --> 00:10:55.446
I'll say this to Dave, you know.

00:10:55.446 --> 00:10:56.280
Yeah, no, for sure.

00:10:56.280 --> 00:10:56.864
So, like,

00:10:56.864 --> 00:10:57.490
I thought maybe

00:10:57.490 --> 00:10:58.866
it was like a joke or something.

00:10:58.866 --> 00:11:00.076
Maybe it was like a psy-op on me

00:11:00.076 --> 00:11:01.911
or something. I don't even know.

00:11:01.911 --> 00:11:03.371
And then, but the, you know,

00:11:03.371 --> 00:11:04.288
near 40 people

00:11:04.288 --> 00:11:07.333
we talk to a lot of the guys

00:11:07.333 --> 00:11:09.043
I've known my entire career and like,

00:11:09.043 --> 00:11:09.960
they wouldn't lie to me.

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:12.797
I have like a friendship with them

00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:13.464
and for them

00:11:13.464 --> 00:11:15.132
to, you know,

00:11:15.132 --> 00:11:16.759
disclose to me that kind of stuff.

00:11:16.759 --> 00:11:18.636
And it ends up being a false,

00:11:18.636 --> 00:11:19.845
would have totally torpedoed

00:11:19.845 --> 00:11:20.471
the friendship.

00:11:20.471 --> 00:11:22.598
And I also went out of my way

00:11:22.598 --> 00:11:23.224
to find people

00:11:23.224 --> 00:11:24.684
who don't know each other either.

00:11:24.684 --> 00:11:26.936
And I had other

00:11:26.936 --> 00:11:27.520
high ranking

00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:28.270
colleagues of mine

00:11:28.270 --> 00:11:29.605
go talk to other people

00:11:29.605 --> 00:11:31.816
that I didn't even personally talk to.

00:11:31.816 --> 00:11:32.400
That group,

00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:32.775
of course,

00:11:32.775 --> 00:11:33.734
we took all that

00:11:33.734 --> 00:11:34.944
and I'm like all the people

00:11:34.944 --> 00:11:37.029
who conducted those interviews.

00:11:37.029 --> 00:11:38.322
I made them get interviewed

00:11:38.322 --> 00:11:39.699
by the inspector general

00:11:39.699 --> 00:11:41.951
because we're crossing our T's here

00:11:41.951 --> 00:11:43.744
because this shit is crazy.

00:11:43.744 --> 00:11:45.746
And I was

00:11:45.746 --> 00:11:46.706
I mean, you can never be perfect,

00:11:46.706 --> 00:11:48.499
but I mean, I was so frickin careful

00:11:48.499 --> 00:11:49.125
to make sure

00:11:49.125 --> 00:11:50.751
I wasn't getting fed some bullshit.

00:11:50.751 --> 00:11:51.919
If they were in coordination

00:11:51.919 --> 00:11:53.462
together on a disinfo campaign,

00:11:53.462 --> 00:11:54.213
holy fuck,

00:11:54.213 --> 00:11:55.423
I shouldn't even be an intel officer

00:11:55.423 --> 00:11:56.132
because I should have,

00:11:56.132 --> 00:11:57.967
you know, sniffed that shit out. So.

00:11:57.967 --> 00:11:59.844
In the last couple of years,

00:11:59.844 --> 00:12:01.846
have you had incidences

00:12:01.846 --> 00:12:03.639
that have caused you to be in fear

00:12:03.639 --> 00:12:04.724
for your life

00:12:04.724 --> 00:12:06.684
for addressing these issues?

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:09.812
Yes, personally.

00:12:10.479 --> 00:12:12.106
There's a Chris Mellon story

00:12:12.106 --> 00:12:12.940
where he's

00:12:12.940 --> 00:12:13.816
supposed to meet

00:12:13.816 --> 00:12:15.109
with somebody on the program

00:12:15.109 --> 00:12:16.819
and he has the meeting all set up

00:12:16.819 --> 00:12:19.071
and two weeks before the meeting,

00:12:19.071 --> 00:12:20.030
he says that the guy just

00:12:20.030 --> 00:12:21.282
randomly has a heart attack.

00:12:21.282 --> 00:12:22.825
We were about two weeks

00:12:22.825 --> 00:12:25.077
away from meeting when he died,

00:12:25.077 --> 00:12:26.495
when he had a heart attack.

00:12:26.495 --> 00:12:27.246
What was the last

00:12:27.246 --> 00:12:28.873
special access program that leaked?

00:12:28.873 --> 00:12:30.082
They don't generally leak.

00:12:30.082 --> 00:12:30.458
People are like,

00:12:30.458 --> 00:12:31.292
Oh, dude, wouldn't it

00:12:31.292 --> 00:12:32.626
be broadly leaked or whatever?

00:12:32.626 --> 00:12:33.335
I'm like,

00:12:33.335 --> 00:12:35.713
as somebody who is super cleared

00:12:35.713 --> 00:12:37.548
to a lot of that conventional stuff

00:12:37.548 --> 00:12:40.009
over the years, stuff never leaks.

00:12:40.009 --> 00:12:41.135
Yeah, it doesn't come out.

00:12:41.135 --> 00:12:42.303
There are plenty of things

00:12:42.303 --> 00:12:43.387
that are pretty serious.

00:12:43.387 --> 00:12:44.930
They're broad

00:12:44.930 --> 00:12:46.932
that have never seen the light of day.

00:12:46.932 --> 00:12:47.475
Of course,

00:12:47.475 --> 00:12:48.684
like you're going to tell someone

00:12:48.684 --> 00:12:49.935
that their entire life

00:12:49.935 --> 00:12:51.687
and their family and their kids like

00:12:51.687 --> 00:12:52.688
everything is in danger.

00:12:52.688 --> 00:12:54.565
It's it doesn't feel too far

00:12:54.565 --> 00:12:55.065
fetched that

00:12:55.065 --> 00:12:56.650
someone will keep a secret,

00:12:56.650 --> 00:12:58.611
that if it threatens their life.

00:12:58.611 --> 00:12:59.111
Look, dude,

00:12:59.111 --> 00:13:00.696
you're not getting promoted.

00:13:00.696 --> 00:13:01.822
You're going to lose your job.

00:13:01.822 --> 00:13:04.033
You know,
the psychology of the typical career

00:13:04.033 --> 00:13:05.075
government worker, right?

00:13:05.075 --> 00:13:07.661
Stable paycheck, pension

00:13:07.661 --> 00:13:08.954
maintained clearance.

00:13:08.954 --> 00:13:11.540
So if any of that's threatened,

00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:12.750
you know, they're going to

00:13:12.750 --> 00:13:14.502
capitulate in most cases. Right.

00:13:14.502 --> 00:13:15.795
The threatening nature

00:13:15.795 --> 00:13:17.296
of some of their indoctrination

00:13:17.296 --> 00:13:18.839
where they're like, this is treason.

00:13:18.839 --> 00:13:19.840
You're going to Leavenworth

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:21.217
if you ever tell anybody

00:13:21.217 --> 00:13:22.301
not in the program.

00:13:22.301 --> 00:13:23.135
And oh, by the way,

00:13:23.135 --> 00:13:24.345
what's the penalty for treason?

00:13:24.345 --> 00:13:25.888
Oh, right. Execution. Right.

00:13:25.888 --> 00:13:27.473
And I was like, well, of well,

00:13:27.473 --> 00:13:27.807
fuck it,

00:13:27.807 --> 00:13:29.475
I'll be the mouthpiece for you.

00:13:29.475 --> 00:13:30.976
I'll be the leader,

00:13:30.976 --> 00:13:33.312
I guess, and I will shepherd

00:13:33.312 --> 00:13:35.564
you privately to the appropriate people

00:13:35.564 --> 00:13:36.565
that could be a recipient

00:13:36.565 --> 00:13:37.358
of your disclosure.

00:13:37.358 --> 00:13:39.360
You don't have to go public,

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:41.946
but I'll do the thing.

00:13:41.946 --> 00:13:44.406
I mean, you know, it's not just me

00:13:44.406 --> 00:13:45.241
that,

00:13:45.241 --> 00:13:46.158
you know, as

00:13:46.158 --> 00:13:48.369
come forward, really, because, I mean,

00:13:48.369 --> 00:13:49.829
Schumer, Rubio,

00:13:49.829 --> 00:13:51.038
all those guys are like, woke

00:13:51.038 --> 00:13:53.165
a bunch of freaking high level

00:13:53.165 --> 00:13:54.959
officers came to us

00:13:54.959 --> 00:13:56.377
and either they're crazy

00:13:56.377 --> 00:13:57.419
or this shit's real.

00:13:57.419 --> 00:13:59.088
Most of these people at some point

00:13:59.088 --> 00:14:00.548
or maybe even currently

00:14:00.548 --> 00:14:02.132
have held very high clearances

00:14:02.132 --> 00:14:03.008
and high positions

00:14:03.008 --> 00:14:03.968
within our government.

00:14:03.968 --> 00:14:05.261
And then Schumer was compelled

00:14:05.261 --> 00:14:05.594
to write

00:14:05.594 --> 00:14:08.931
that big 64 page amendment that talks

00:14:09.139 --> 00:14:12.434
no shit, non-human tech, recoveries

00:14:12.518 --> 00:14:14.103
and you have the majority leader who’s

00:14:14.103 --> 00:14:15.187
tight with the president

00:14:15.187 --> 00:14:16.856
putting out a law

00:14:16.856 --> 00:14:17.731
that will be signed here

00:14:17.731 --> 00:14:18.607
hopefully this fall

00:14:18.607 --> 00:14:21.151
that really puts the fucking executive

00:14:21.151 --> 00:14:23.737
in a bind. Yeah. So

00:14:23.821 --> 00:14:24.488
I don't

00:14:24.488 --> 00:14:26.198
think that that was done in a vacuum.

00:14:28.450 --> 00:14:29.201
I think the one thing

00:14:29.201 --> 00:14:29.910
that can get the left

00:14:29.910 --> 00:14:30.786
and the right together

00:14:30.786 --> 00:14:31.579
is bloat

00:14:31.579 --> 00:14:33.831
in the military industrial complex

00:14:34.999 --> 00:14:36.500
And you know, yeah, nobody likes that.

00:14:36.500 --> 00:14:38.794
I don't think members of Congress

00:14:38.794 --> 00:14:39.670
don't like getting the door

00:14:39.670 --> 00:14:40.462
shut on them either.

00:14:40.462 --> 00:14:41.005
So they want

00:14:41.005 --> 00:14:42.131
they want that information

00:14:42.131 --> 00:14:44.300
because they represent the constituency

00:14:44.300 --> 00:14:45.801
And that was the Matt Gaetz story.

00:14:45.801 --> 00:14:46.760
Several months ago

00:14:46.760 --> 00:14:47.636
my office received

00:14:47.636 --> 00:14:49.096
a protected disclosure

00:14:49.096 --> 00:14:51.307
from Eglin Air Force Base indicating

00:14:51.307 --> 00:14:52.975
that there was a UAP incident

00:14:52.975 --> 00:14:54.560
that required my attention.

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:57.438
We were not afforded access

00:14:57.438 --> 00:14:58.731
to all of the flight crew,

00:14:58.731 --> 00:15:00.399
who was basically denied access

00:15:00.399 --> 00:15:01.483
to a crew

00:15:01.483 --> 00:15:02.401
that had seen kind of a

00:15:02.401 --> 00:15:05.487
diamond shaped formation of orbs.

00:15:05.654 --> 00:15:07.573
He should be fully clued into,

00:15:07.573 --> 00:15:08.449
if you know,

00:15:08.449 --> 00:15:10.159
it is terrestrial in origin

00:15:10.159 --> 00:15:12.536
because he's he's he's on the

00:15:12.620 --> 00:15:14.413
Armed Services Committee.

00:15:14.413 --> 00:15:15.873
If you could just name

00:15:15.873 --> 00:15:19.710
anything titles, programs, departments,

00:15:19.793 --> 00:15:21.337
regions, I'd be happy

00:15:21.337 --> 00:15:21.921
to give you that

00:15:21.921 --> 00:15:22.963
in a enclosed environment.

00:15:22.963 --> 00:15:24.465
I can tell you specifically.

00:15:24.465 --> 00:15:25.257
Thank you.

00:15:25.257 --> 00:15:26.342
Maybe in a

00:15:26.342 --> 00:15:27.468
if we could

00:15:27.468 --> 00:15:30.095
get in a confidential area SCIF

00:15:30.095 --> 00:15:31.221
we can talk about that.

00:15:31.221 --> 00:15:34.058
But unfortunately we were denied access

00:15:34.058 --> 00:15:35.184
to the SCIF.

00:15:35.184 --> 00:15:36.602
A lot of the narrative

00:15:36.602 --> 00:15:37.311
for the whole thing

00:15:37.311 --> 00:15:38.771
was that you were denied a SCIF.

00:15:38.771 --> 00:15:39.521
What does SCIF stand

00:15:39.521 --> 00:15:40.564
for just for people.

00:15:40.564 --> 00:15:42.024
It was a specialized

00:15:42.024 --> 00:15:44.151
compartmented information facility,

00:15:44.151 --> 00:15:44.985
which basically means

00:15:44.985 --> 00:15:45.402
that you guys

00:15:45.402 --> 00:15:46.570
would just get into a secure,

00:15:46.570 --> 00:15:48.864
secure place where you can share.

00:15:48.864 --> 00:15:49.698
Yeah, that's,

00:15:49.698 --> 00:15:50.574
you know, a facility

00:15:50.574 --> 00:15:52.576
that's accredited to talk at,

00:15:52.576 --> 00:15:53.077
you know,

00:15:53.077 --> 00:15:54.203
top secret, sensitive,

00:15:54.203 --> 00:15:56.538
compartmented information level.

00:15:56.538 --> 00:15:57.247
And yeah,

00:15:57.247 --> 00:15:58.832
the members are pretty incensed that

00:15:58.832 --> 00:15:59.625
I believe it was like

00:15:59.625 --> 00:16:01.335
they couldn't reserve a SCIF

00:16:01.335 --> 00:16:01.877
and then they couldn't

00:16:01.877 --> 00:16:03.420
give me a one time

00:16:03.420 --> 00:16:05.381
read on back into the right accesses.

00:16:05.381 --> 00:16:06.632
Since I left the government.

00:16:06.632 --> 00:16:07.675
Do you have any sense of why

00:16:07.675 --> 00:16:08.550
that was denied?

00:16:08.550 --> 00:16:09.301
I don't know.

00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:10.302
No, I don't really have insight.

00:16:10.302 --> 00:16:13.055
It was something they mentioned to me,

00:16:13.055 --> 00:16:15.015
you know, it was security or something,

00:16:15.015 --> 00:16:17.184
denied it.

00:16:17.267 --> 00:16:19.770
If you believe we have crashed craft,

00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:20.813
as stated earlier,

00:16:20.813 --> 00:16:22.648
do we have the bodies of the pilots

00:16:22.648 --> 00:16:24.775
who piloted this craft?

00:16:24.775 --> 00:16:25.526
As I've stated

00:16:25.526 --> 00:16:26.235
publicly already

00:16:26.235 --> 00:16:26.652
in my News

00:16:26.652 --> 00:16:27.653
Nation interview,

00:16:27.653 --> 00:16:28.779
Biologics came

00:16:28.779 --> 00:16:30.155
with some of these recoveries.

00:16:30.155 --> 00:16:33.117
Yeah.

00:16:33.117 --> 00:16:33.701
Were they,

00:16:33.701 --> 00:16:36.203
I guess, human or non-human biologics?

00:16:36.912 --> 00:16:37.538
Non-human.

00:16:37.538 --> 00:16:39.289
And that was the assessment of people

00:16:39.289 --> 00:16:39.999
with direct knowledge

00:16:39.999 --> 00:16:40.916
on the program I talked to

00:16:40.916 --> 00:16:41.542
that are currently

00:16:41.542 --> 00:16:42.376
still on the program.

00:16:42.376 --> 00:16:43.627
We had

00:16:43.627 --> 00:16:44.920
one sort of bombshell

00:16:44.920 --> 00:16:45.963
sound bite from the hearing

00:16:45.963 --> 00:16:46.714
as Congresswoman

00:16:46.714 --> 00:16:49.216
Nancy Mace asked you about biologics.

00:16:49.216 --> 00:16:50.884
Ross Coulthart in the News Nation

00:16:50.884 --> 00:16:53.262
interview asked you about pilots

00:16:53.262 --> 00:16:54.847
coming out of these crafts.

00:16:54.847 --> 00:16:55.931
Do you want to just speak to that

00:16:55.931 --> 00:16:57.224
a little bit?

00:16:57.224 --> 00:16:57.558
Yeah.

00:16:57.558 --> 00:16:58.142
I mean, it's

00:16:58.142 --> 00:17:00.936
it is a mind blowing side of it, right?

00:17:00.936 --> 00:17:02.896
It's a little easy to imagine,

00:17:02.896 --> 00:17:04.565
you know, an artifact or whatever.

00:17:04.565 --> 00:17:05.774
But when you

00:17:05.774 --> 00:17:07.109
start talking about,

00:17:07.109 --> 00:17:10.154
you know, the biological side of it,

00:17:10.154 --> 00:17:10.946
it really throws you

