00:22:48.700 --> 00:22:50.077
of current projects,

00:22:50.077 --> 00:22:50.952
and therefore,

00:22:50.952 --> 00:22:52.871
if directed, should be set up

00:22:52.871 --> 00:22:56.208
independently of existing projects.

00:22:56.291 --> 00:22:56.958
If you were

00:22:56.958 --> 00:22:58.710
