00:23:28.782 --> 00:23:29.950
Holy crap, that's crazy.

00:23:29.950 --> 00:23:31.076
You know,
there's like a whole other side of

00:23:31.076 --> 00:23:32.619
Manhattan project.

00:23:32.619 --> 00:23:34.413
This is a wild revelation.

00:23:34.413 --> 00:23:35.664
Blue Book was the Air Force's

00:23:35.664 --> 00:23:36.665
official program

00:23:36.665 --> 00:23:38.542
