00:24:25.505 --> 00:24:26.465
Well, the first hint

00:24:26.465 --> 00:24:27.883
we get might actually come

00:24:27.883 --> 00:24:29.885
from the quintessential UFO story,

00:24:29.885 --> 00:24:32.888
the Roswell crash in 1947.

00:24:32.888 --> 00:24:35.557
As the story goes, in 1947,

00:24:35.557 --> 00:24:36.725
mysterious debris

00:24:36.725 --> 00:24:38.185
from a crash was retrieved

00:24:38.185 --> 00:24:40.395
