00:24:40.395 --> 00:24:42.105
After collecting the wreckage,

00:24:42.105 --> 00:24:43.190
the Roswell Army

00:24:43.190 --> 00:24:45.609
Airfield issued a pretty insane

00:24:45.609 --> 00:24:46.735
press release

00:24:46.735 --> 00:24:47.360
stating that

00:24:47.360 --> 00:24:48.320
a flying disc

00:24:48.320 --> 00:24:50.655
had been retrieved from a local ranch.

00:24:50.655 --> 00:24:52.115
But within 24 hours,

00:24:52.115 --> 00:24:53.033
the military announced

00:24:53.033 --> 00:24:53.742
that the saucer

00:24:53.742 --> 00:24:54.784
had actually just been

00:24:54.784 --> 00:24:56.953
a weather balloon.

00:24:56.953 --> 00:24:58.663
Cut to 1978.

00:24:58.663 --> 00:24:59.539
Lieutenant Colonel

00:24:59.539 --> 00:25:01.875
Jesse Marcel said that this was all

00:25:01.875 --> 00:25:03.502
just a cover story

00:25:03.502 --> 00:25:04.961
to divert public attention

00:25:04.961 --> 00:25:06.463
