00:25:11.801 --> 00:25:14.012
and malleable memory metal.

00:25:14.012 --> 00:25:14.888
According to him,

00:25:14.888 --> 00:25:15.555
the materials

00:25:15.555 --> 00:25:16.598
were eventually taken

00:25:16.598 --> 00:25:17.557
to Wright-Patterson

00:25:17.557 --> 00:25:19.392
Air Force Base in Ohio.

00:25:19.392 --> 00:25:20.894
This actually makes sense.

00:25:20.894 --> 00:25:22.354
Wright Pat was the place

00:25:22.354 --> 00:25:23.063
that the military

00:25:23.063 --> 00:25:24.523
would take enemy equipment

00:25:24.523 --> 00:25:26.525
in order to reverse engineer it.

00:25:26.525 --> 00:25:28.902
In fact, just a few years earlier,

00:25:28.902 --> 00:25:29.861
the base was used

00:25:29.861 --> 00:25:31.780
to successfully reverse engineer

00:25:31.780 --> 00:25:33.823
a German pulse jet engine.

00:25:33.823 --> 00:25:35.534
When prominent elected government

00:25:35.534 --> 00:25:36.910
representatives would ask

00:25:36.910 --> 00:25:38.828
what was going on at Wright-Patterson,

00:25:38.828 --> 00:25:39.996
they would get shut down.

00:25:39.996 --> 00:25:41.623
