00:31:37.395 --> 00:31:39.147
Over the past 37 years,

00:31:39.147 --> 00:31:40.899
I have personally located

00:31:40.899 --> 00:31:41.774
and interviewed

00:31:41.774 --> 00:31:44.360
more than 120 of these former

00:31:44.360 --> 00:31:46.154
or retired military personnel.

00:31:46.154 --> 00:31:47.864
You have Robert Salas

00:31:47.864 --> 00:31:49.198
