00:31:58.791 --> 00:32:00.418
Yeah the sights were going down,

00:32:00.418 --> 00:32:01.419
like one by one.

00:32:01.419 --> 00:32:03.671
Very rarely does a missile malfunction.

00:32:03.671 --> 00:32:06.174
And I don't think any much more rare of

00:32:06.174 --> 00:32:08.051
this would be two at the same time.

00:32:08.051 --> 00:32:09.177
But never ten.

00:32:09.177 --> 00:32:10.303
You have Bob Jacobs

00:32:10.303 --> 00:32:11.721
