00:32:40.291 --> 00:32:41.793
Well, I know the missileers,

00:32:41.793 --> 00:32:42.335
you know,

00:32:42.335 --> 00:32:43.962
they're on what they call PRP,

00:32:43.962 --> 00:32:45.672
