00:32:45.672 --> 00:32:46.839
Like they have to, like, report

00:32:46.839 --> 00:32:47.465
if they're like, you know,

00:32:47.465 --> 00:32:48.424
take an ibuprofen,

00:32:48.424 --> 00:32:49.467
for God's sakes, because,

00:32:49.467 --> 00:32:50.468
you know, they're a key turner

00:32:50.468 --> 00:32:52.220
for nuclear weapons.

00:32:52.220 --> 00:32:53.137
These missileers

00:32:53.137 --> 00:32:53.846
go through the most

00:32:53.846 --> 00:32:55.223
stringent of mental health

00:32:55.223 --> 00:32:56.766
exams to get their jobs.

00:32:56.766 --> 00:32:58.476
They're literally the people we task

00:32:58.476 --> 00:32:59.352
with hitting the button

00:32:59.352 --> 00:33:00.520
that sends a nuke.

00:33:00.520 --> 00:33:01.562
By definition,

00:33:01.562 --> 00:33:03.523
they're the picture of mental health.

00:33:03.523 --> 00:33:05.650
And they are all steeped in a culture

00:33:05.650 --> 00:33:07.694
that frowns upon attention seeking.

00:33:07.694 --> 00:33:08.695
Time and time again,

00:33:08.695 --> 00:33:09.237
these missile

00:33:09.237 --> 00:33:10.530
men would see UFOs

00:33:10.530 --> 00:33:11.864
