00:34:22.977 --> 00:34:23.811
I mean, it's

00:34:23.811 --> 00:34:25.938
so hard because to put yourself

00:34:25.938 --> 00:34:27.356
in a different sentient’s shoes

00:34:27.356 --> 00:34:28.941
to understand intent and

00:34:29.025 --> 00:34:30.401
all that, I mean,

