00:34:52.006 --> 00:34:54.592
I mean, without having,

00:34:54.592 --> 00:34:55.259
you know, a

00:34:55.259 --> 00:34:56.803
penetration into their ooda loop

00:34:56.803 --> 00:34:58.596
