00:34:58.596 --> 00:35:02.183
Yeah, it could be all of the above.

00:35:02.266 --> 00:35:02.767
Yeah.

00:35:02.767 --> 00:35:04.310
And it's really impossible

00:35:04.310 --> 00:35:05.978
to really ever gauge intent.

00:35:08.648 --> 00:35:09.607
The controller told us

00:35:09.607 --> 00:35:10.566
that these objects

00:35:10.566 --> 00:35:11.859
had been observed for over two weeks

00:35:11.859 --> 00:35:12.610
