00:35:17.949 --> 00:35:18.825
For those don't realize,

00:35:18.825 --> 00:35:21.119
above 80,000 feet is space.

00:35:22.036 --> 00:35:23.412
It's just this cat and mouse

00:35:23.412 --> 00:35:24.580
sort of

00:35:24.580 --> 00:35:26.582
recursive unsolvability

00:35:26.582 --> 00:35:28.501
where it's just very hard to classify.

00:35:28.501 --> 00:35:29.836
It's almost like playing with you

00:35:29.836 --> 00:35:30.169
