00:35:51.149 --> 00:35:53.317
that had their own kind of up

00:35:53.317 --> 00:35:54.610
close kind of sightings.

00:35:54.610 --> 00:35:57.155
They said that they got that vibe, too,

00:35:57.155 --> 00:35:57.780
You know,
who knows

00:35:57.780 --> 00:36:00.658
if that's psychosomatic or what.

00:36:00.658 --> 00:36:01.784
But they did they

00:36:01.784 --> 00:36:03.161
they did get a vibe like that too.

00:36:03.161 --> 00:36:04.328
When you stare into the abyss

00:36:04.328 --> 00:36:05.955
