00:36:05.955 --> 00:36:06.706
Yeah, exactly.

00:36:06.706 --> 00:36:07.665
And then, of course,

00:36:07.665 --> 00:36:09.500
I've had a very smart guy

00:36:09.500 --> 00:36:10.543
