00:36:15.089 --> 00:36:17.925
And it's like they observe,

00:36:17.925 --> 00:36:19.427
they don't really care.

00:36:19.427 --> 00:36:20.803
And they don't really care to interact,

00:36:20.803 --> 00:36:22.013
but they're just here to observe.

00:36:22.013 --> 00:36:23.431
But is that your bias, that it's

00:36:23.431 --> 00:36:25.850
sort of an anthropological

00:36:25.933 --> 00:36:27.852
zoological model where

00:36:27.852 --> 00:36:29.312
