00:37:28.579 --> 00:37:29.622
a little more attention

00:37:37.964 --> 00:37:38.506
To the extent

00:37:38.506 --> 00:37:39.590
that there is interference,

00:37:39.590 --> 00:37:40.883
I think one anomaly

00:37:40.883 --> 00:37:41.842
that's important to talk about

00:37:41.842 --> 00:37:42.802
is it
seems to be like

00:37:42.802 --> 00:37:43.302
there's a lot

00:37:43.302 --> 00:37:45.680
of electromagnetic radiation

00:37:45.680 --> 00:37:48.015
that comes off of these crafts.

00:37:48.015 --> 00:37:50.393
And I remember talking to Gary Nolan

00:37:50.393 --> 00:37:51.727
and he mentioned

00:37:51.727 --> 00:37:52.603
that he was kind of given

00:37:52.603 --> 00:37:55.690
a file by the CIA and he was

00:37:55.690 --> 00:37:57.191
