00:38:13.040 --> 00:38:15.668
What became known as Havana Syndrome.

00:38:15.668 --> 00:38:17.295
And in both cases,

00:38:17.295 --> 00:38:18.379
you have this kind of

00:38:18.379 --> 00:38:19.964
severe electromagnetic

00:38:19.964 --> 00:38:23.217
radiation effects and often

00:38:23.301 --> 00:38:25.177
differences in the caudate

00:38:25.177 --> 00:38:26.470
nucleus and putamen,

00:38:26.470 --> 00:38:27.722
which is in the basal ganglia,

00:38:27.722 --> 00:38:29.765
the dorsal striatum of the brain,

00:38:29.765 --> 00:38:30.850
the scarring,

00:38:30.850 --> 00:38:32.768
but also the neuronal density

00:38:32.768 --> 00:38:34.061
