01:41:22.826 --> 01:41:25.079
if this is a thing that we acknowledge.

01:41:25.079 --> 01:41:26.413
And once again,

01:41:26.413 --> 01:41:28.207
nuclear physics, broadly studied.

01:41:28.207 --> 01:41:30.167
Nuclear weapons development,

01:41:30.167 --> 01:41:31.543
that's classified.

01:41:31.543 --> 01:41:33.545
So that's and that's all I have to say.

01:41:33.545 --> 01:41:34.755
It just said, just come on.

01:41:34.755 --> 01:41:35.589
Do you think in some ways

01:41:35.589 --> 01:41:38.133
