01:41:54.942 --> 01:41:56.693
And, you know, we've to be careful.

01:41:56.693 --> 01:41:57.903
Watch your step.

01:41:57.903 --> 01:41:59.863
Or they can be incredibly libertarian

01:41:59.863 --> 01:42:01.865
