maybe as we thought that they were.

01:42:07.246 --> 01:42:09.081
And, you know,

01:42:09.081 --> 01:42:09.790
I think it could go in

01:42:09.790 --> 01:42:10.749
either direction. Yeah.

01:42:10.749 --> 01:42:11.583
Or it's just like

01:42:11.583 --> 01:42:12.459
they're just simply waiting

01:42:12.459 --> 01:42:14.670
