01:42:14.670 --> 01:42:15.712
about that.

01:42:15.712 --> 01:42:16.672
We've just like

01:42:16.672 --> 01:42:18.048
we look at it we're like, huh

01:42:18.048 --> 01:42:18.924
that's interesting.

01:42:18.924 --> 01:42:20.300
And then we go about our day

01:42:20.300 --> 01:42:22.010
and then we don't even integrate

01:42:22.010 --> 01:42:24.221
the phenomenon into our lives

01:42:29.226 --> 01:42:31.812
