01:43:20.611 --> 01:43:21.195
finally getting

01:43:21.195 --> 01:43:22.654
into the information flow.

01:43:24.698 --> 01:43:25.365
In her book,

01:43:25.365 --> 01:43:27.451
American Cosmic, Diana Pasulka

01:43:27.451 --> 01:43:29.411
makes the pretty convincing case

01:43:29.411 --> 01:43:31.205
that many seemingly divine

01:43:31.205 --> 01:43:33.457
contact experiences in the past

01:43:33.457 --> 01:43:35.167
could have actually been what we now

01:43:35.167 --> 01:43:36.793
call UFO experiences.

01:43:36.793 --> 01:43:38.086
Just take the case of Saint

01:43:38.086 --> 01:43:39.213
Francis of Assisi.

01:43:39.213 --> 01:43:39.796
His close

01:43:39.796 --> 01:43:41.965
confidant, Brother Leo, documents

01:43:41.965 --> 01:43:43.759
the experience describing

01:43:43.759 --> 01:43:46.511
and fury, creating atmospheric sparks,

01:43:46.511 --> 01:43:47.679
a spinning disk,

01:43:47.679 --> 01:43:49.264
telepathic communication

01:43:49.264 --> 01:43:50.891
between Francis and the disc.

01:43:50.891 --> 01:43:52.726
And then Francis is wounded

01:43:52.726 --> 01:43:53.977
by rays of light.

01:43:53.977 --> 01:43:56.146
Francis interprets these hand wounds

01:43:56.146 --> 01:43:57.898
